    {
      "id": "PKri",
      "code_hash": "fd28f8df52b1f3e12cc586916ee58da1",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"basis-vectors-and-signature\">Basis Vectors and Signature</h2></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
    {
      "id": "Xref",
      "code_hash": "483815862ac3678c2d97e87aebe16424",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/html": "<div style='display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: normal;flex-wrap: nowrap;gap: 0.5rem'><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">\u03b3\u2080\u00b2 = <code>1</code> (timelike)</span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">\u03b3\u2081\u00b2 = <code>-1</code> (spacelike)</span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">\u03b3\u2082\u00b2 = <code>-1</code> (spacelike)</span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">\u03b3\u2083\u00b2 = <code>-1</code> (spacelike)</span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">Pseudoscalar I = <code>\ud835\udc70</code></span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">I\u00b2 = <code>-1</code></span></span></div>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SFPL",
      "code_hash": "b8c4fff1d1523059a74c6e23d61b2829",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"bivectors-boosts-and-rotations\">Bivectors \u2014 Boosts and Rotations</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">In STA, bivectors split into two types:</span>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Timelike bivectors</strong> (<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(\\gamma_0 \\gamma_i||)</marimo-tex>): generate Lorentz boosts</li>\n<li><strong>Spacelike bivectors</strong> (<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(\\gamma_i \\gamma_j||)</marimo-tex>): generate spatial rotations</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
    {
      "id": "BYtC",
      "code_hash": "03b2178d3898ec0386f25859308fb1bf",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/html": "<div style='display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: normal;flex-wrap: nowrap;gap: 0.5rem'><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Boost generators</strong> (square to <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(+1||)</marimo-tex>):</span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>$(\\gamma_0 \\gamma_1)^2 = $ <code>1</code></li>\n</ul></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>$(\\gamma_0 \\gamma_2)^2 = $ <code>1</code></li>\n</ul></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>$(\\gamma_0 \\gamma_3)^2 = $ <code>1</code></li>\n</ul></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Rotation generators</strong> (square to <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(-1||)</marimo-tex>):</span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>$(\\gamma_1 \\gamma_2)^2 = $ <code>-1</code></li>\n</ul></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>$(\\gamma_1 \\gamma_3)^2 = $ <code>-1</code></li>\n</ul></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>$(\\gamma_2 \\gamma_3)^2 = $ <code>-1</code></li>\n</ul></span></div>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
    {
      "id": "RGSE",
      "code_hash": "38095a2161efce211efc9148db63aa7c",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"interactive-lorentz-boost\">Interactive Lorentz Boost</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">A boost in the <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(\\gamma_0 \\gamma_1||)</marimo-tex> plane with rapidity <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(\\varphi||)</marimo-tex>:</span>\n<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||[R = \\cosh(\\varphi/2) + \\sinh(\\varphi/2)\\, \\gamma_0 \\gamma_1||]</marimo-tex><span class=\"paragraph\">The sandwich product <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(R \\gamma_0 \\tilde{R}||)</marimo-tex> boosts the rest-frame\ntimelike vector into a moving frame.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
