        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"relative-vectors-pauli-algebra\">Relative Vectors (Pauli Algebra)</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">The relative (spatial) vectors are <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(\\sigma_i = \\gamma_i \\gamma_0||)</marimo-tex>.\nThese are bivectors in STA but behave like the Pauli matrices:\n<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(\\sigma_i^2 = 1||)</marimo-tex>, <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(\\sigma_i \\sigma_j = -\\sigma_j \\sigma_i||)</marimo-tex> for <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(i \\neq j||)</marimo-tex>.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
